{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e125cf2249","title":"关于举办学习班的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6a8bf1fbb1","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"e125cf2249"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"09023e28ab","type":"paragraph","text":"我们坚决支持你们。我们两国是唇齿相依的邻邦，我们两国人民是休戚与共的兄弟。兄弟的越南南方人民和全体越南人民可以相信，你们的斗争就是我们的斗争。七亿中国人民是越南人民的坚强后盾，辽阔的中国领土是越南人民可靠的后方。在我们两国人民坚强的战斗团结面前，美帝国主义的任何军事冒险和政治欺骗都是注定要失败的。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"537cc699aa","type":"paragraph","text":"胜利-定属于英雄的越南人民","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"b364c6e902","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"8505de3e45","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年十二月十九日关于举办学习班的指示","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"108cdcad40","type":"paragraph","text":"（-九六七年十月一九六八年二月）中央应该开，主要是各省开，不仅军队开，地方党政文教也要集训。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"48b7f03761","type":"paragraph","text":"大X","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"ef9919c296","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"af46033fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"造反派也要训，他们坐不下来，心野了，一期不行，可以训练两期、三期。造反派人很多，我看训练的办法好。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"98752f9571","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"c9f68149af","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"627b53c351","type":"paragraph","text":"X军队办学习班，要有战七参加。","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"42ad522fa2","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"aa5564fde0","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"0216d634c8","type":"paragraph","text":"X办学习班，是个好办法，很多问题可以在学习班得到解决。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"0174793502","type":"paragraph","text":"（转引自九六八年二月五日《人民日报》、《解放军报》","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"},{"id":"25b7726a7a","type":"paragraph","text":"社论：《华北山河-·片红》）·344。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249"}],"page":{"id":"7913edc30a","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e125cf2249","start":357,"end":357}}}},"__N_SSG":true}